{"tid":2414612,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"玄彬放閃冧女友孫藝珍：現在努力守護愛情","createTime":"2021-02-19T14:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T19:01:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec8a24aaefb82fa2a9920ffa9f405eaa2d90cf62","tid":2414612,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/woX3A7XLKNp6mrxi7T2AcmplVn4=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VREIFMUYANA5DAGZIFV27HGHFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwoX3A7XLKNp6mrxi7T2AcmplVn4%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVREIFMUYANA5DAGZIFV27HGHFE.jpg&h=e6a2a085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國38歲型男玄彬於今年元旦日認戀《愛的迫降》拍檔孫藝珍，愛情、事業兩得意，除了即將開拍的電影《秘密任務2》外，廣告代言、雜誌訪問忙過不停。<br />\n<br />\n滿意操肌成果<br />\n玄彬早前以運動look拍攝雜誌《GQ Korea》新相，大晒麒麟臂，而相關的訪問亦於今日曝光，據悉拍攝當日，玄彬的確拿着器材邊做運動邊拍攝，他亦笑言運動量很大，隨後他又指自己特別喜歡用啞鈴操肌，對於自己的闊膊頭都相當滿意。<br />\n<br />\n提起《愛的迫降》熱潮持續，日本甚至有相關的展覽，玄彬感謝fans的喜愛，亦指因疫情無法跟fans見面而感到可惜。對於年紀，玄彬坦言：「總以為踏入3字頭就會有很大變化，但其實都沒有太大分別，只是在人際關係及工作方面多了一些從容和包容、接受某種情況的範圍變寬了。」對於愛情，玄彬亦指：「雖說不能沒有，但要守護也不容易，我現在仍努力守護中。」似乎暗地裏提起女友孫藝珍。<br />\n<br />\n暗示與允兒有感情線<br />\n玄彬於《秘密任務2》飾演北韓刑警任鐵零一角，他指想表現出角色與第一集中有所不同，因此苦惱該如何演出。由於《秘密任務2》及《愛的迫降》都以南北韓為背景，玄彬亦被問起女友孫藝珍及拍檔允兒，笑言：「假如任鐵零在南韓遇上尹世理（《愛的迫降》孫藝珍角色）？當然不行，任鐵零要遇上敏英（《秘密任務》允兒角色）才行。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8TSHaLZepjNHpEyHY5bhxN0mZKs=/802x1077/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z6CVD4QO2JEJ5EKH33ZQVRAPQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8TSHaLZepjNHpEyHY5bhxN0mZKs%3D%2F802x1077%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ6CVD4QO2JEJ5EKH33ZQVRAPQE.jpg&h=ddf8d9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/msj-JtxnSImDTxhBjEn6T7zOoqw=/802x1078/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IKHF3WLYXJAGXICU6N4UPE6TC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fmsj-JtxnSImDTxhBjEn6T7zOoqw%3D%2F802x1078%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIKHF3WLYXJAGXICU6N4UPE6TC4.jpg&h=99f0eb1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eU9GujiroxAPsHtg62SYlFxfCuU=/802x531/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X2UTXSEDURCY3IMHIEU32LTGLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeU9GujiroxAPsHtg62SYlFxfCuU%3D%2F802x531%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX2UTXSEDURCY3IMHIEU32LTGLM.jpg&h=dacd30bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/shXzja5OvGJwbKLmqq718qx-RVk=/802x871/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RZ5LKUPVMNAZXAILEAPUE62LZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FshXzja5OvGJwbKLmqq718qx-RVk%3D%2F802x871%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRZ5LKUPVMNAZXAILEAPUE62LZ4.jpg&h=b2d4e345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fg6-C1zQPuntA9NQiS4t1Eezy1I=/802x502/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TPIAPJYGZ5BDNAJ64W2GGXJTRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffg6-C1zQPuntA9NQiS4t1Eezy1I%3D%2F802x502%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTPIAPJYGZ5BDNAJ64W2GGXJTRM.jpg&h=9a7fc010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/enterta